## ğŸ“¦ Installation

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.8+
- Git

### Quick Setup
```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/romiassa/northwind-shipment-dashboard.git
cd northwind-shipment-dashboard

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Linux/Mac
# venv\Scripts\activate   # Windows

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run dashboard
python dashboard/app.py

# Open browser: http://localhost:8050